					<h3>Meets</h3><a name="meets"></a>
					<p>Throught summer we have regular camping meets and in the winter regular hut meets. We also have day walks throughout the year and day climbs in the summer.</p>
					<p>In winter we meet once a week at the Leeds Wall and in summer at a local crag. We often follow this with a trip to the nearest pub.</p>
					<p>We mainly meet in the Lake District, North Wales and the Peak District along with trips to Scotland, Pembrokeshire and occasionally abroad.</p>
					<p>There's more information on what we do and where we meet on the meets page.</p>
							<%= link_to "Meets Page", meets_path, class: "btn btn-lg user-btn" %>
